<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA33">
<l>nakara maruḷpurintu nāṉmukaṟkup pūmēṟ</l>
<l>pakara maṟaippayanta paṇpaṉ – peyariṉaiyē</l>
<l>puntiyāṟ cintiyā tōti yuruveṇṇu</l>
<l>mantiyā lāmpayaṉaṅ keṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not thinking with the mind anything but the names of the excellent one</l>
<l>who graced the four-faced one with an abode on the flower</l>
<l>[and] produced the splendid Vedas, what benefit is there</l>
<l>that comes from [praying at] dusk and dawn, when one recites [and] counts repetitions?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
